::Shredder::

Shredder shakes his head. "Megatron has requested that I interrogate him in 
private," he lies, kicking Quickstrike in the side.

He takes Quickstrike by the leg, dragging him off toward Megatron's quarters.

At the door, he turns to the preds, "I think you should clean up in here. 
Hell Beast might be mad if he finds his ship trashed."
